---
// src/pages/reviews/macbook-neo-review.astro
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout 
  title="MacBook Neo Review 2026 - Apple's Affordable Laptop">
  <article class="review">
    <header class="review-header">
      <span class="category">Laptops</span>
      <h1>MacBook Neo Review 2026: Apple's Most Affordable Laptop</h1>
      <div class="meta">
        <span>By ReviewCloud Team</span>
        <span>•</span>
        <span>March 6, 2026</span>
      </div>
    </header>

    <div class="rating">
      <span class="score">4.5</span>
      <span class="stars">⭐⭐⭐⭐⭐</span>
    </div>

    <div class="price-banner">
      <span class="price">Starting at $599</span>
      <span class="release">Launch: March 11, 2026</span>
    </div>

    <div class="toc">
      <h2>Table of Contents</h2>
      <ul>
        <li><a href="#overview">Overview</a></li>
        <li><a href="#performance">Performance</a></li>
        <li><a href="#design">Design & Display</a></li>
        <li><a href="#battery">Battery Life</a></li>
        <li><a href="#verdict">Verdict      </ul>
</a></li>
    </div>

    <section id="overview">
      <h2>Overview</h2>
      <p>The <strong>MacBook Neo</strong> is Apple's most affordable laptop ever, priced starting at just $599. It features the same A18 Pro chip found in the iPhone 16 Pro, making it a powerful yet budget-friendly option for everyday users.</p>
      <p>Apple positioned the Neo as a direct competitor to Windows PCs and Chromebooks in the affordable laptop market.</p>
    </section>

    <section id="performance">
      <h2>Performance</h2>
      <p>Despite its low price, the MacBook Neo delivers impressive performance thanks to the A18 Pro chip:</p>
      <div class="benchmark-table">
        <table>
          <thead>
            <tr>
              <th>Benchmark</th>
              <th>MacBook Neo</th>
              <th>M1 MacBook Air</th>
            </tr>
          </thead>
          <tbody>
            <tr>
              <td>Single-Core</td>
              <td>3,461</td>
              <td>2,346</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
              <td>Multi-Core</td>
              <td>8,668</td>
              <td>8,342</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
              <td>Metal</td>
              <td>31,286</td>
              <td>33,148</td>
            </tr>
          </tbody>
        </table>
      </div>
      <p>The Neo offers 50% faster performance for everyday tasks compared to the best-selling PC with Intel Core Ultra 5, and up to 2x faster for photo editing.</p>
    </section>

    <section id="design">
      <h2>Design & Display</h2>
      <p>The MacBook Neo features a sleek design similar to other MacBooks, with a focus on portability. It's perfect for students, casual users, and anyone who needs a reliable laptop without breaking the bank.</p>
    </section>

    <section id="battery">
      <h2>Battery Life</h2>
      <p>Apple claims all-day battery life, making it ideal for students and professionals who need to work on the go without constantly searching for power outlets.</p>
    </section>

    <section id="verdict">
      <h2>Verdict</h2>
      <p>The MacBook Neo is an excellent choice for:</p>
      <ul>
        <li>Students on a budget</li>
        <li>First-time Mac users</li>
        <li>Anyone needing a secondary laptop</li>
        <li>Casual users who don't need Pro-level performance</li>
      </ul>
      <div class="buy-links">
        <h3>Where to Buy</h3>
        <a href="https://www.amazon.com/s?k=MacBook+Neo&tag=rc0440-20" class="buy-btn" target="_blank" rel="nofollow">
          Pre-order on Amazon
        </a>
      </div>
    </section>
  </article>
</Layout>

<style>
  .review {
    max-width: 800px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 2rem;
    background: white;
  }

  .review-header {
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }

  .category {
    background: #667eea;
    color: white;
    padding: 0.25rem 0.75rem;
    border-radius: 20px;
    font-size: 0.875rem;
  }

  .review-header h1 {
    font-size: 2rem;
    margin: 1rem 0;
    line-height: 1.2;
  }

  .meta {
    color: #666;
    display: flex;
    gap: 0.5rem;
    justify-content: center;
  }

  .rating {
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
    padding: 1.5rem;
    background: #f8f9fa;
    border-radius: 12px;
  }

  .score {
    font-size: 3rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: #667eea;
  }

  .stars {
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    margin-left: 1rem;
  }

  .price-banner {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: space-between;
    background: #e8f5e9;
    padding: 1rem;
    border-radius: 8px;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }

  .price {
    font-weight: 700;
    color: #2e7d32;
    font-size: 1.25rem;
  }

  .release {
    color: #666;
  }

  .toc {
    background: #f8f9fa;
    padding: 1.5rem;
    border-radius: 12px;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }

  .toc h2 {
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .toc ul {
    list-style: none;
  }

  .toc li {
    padding: 0.5rem 0;
    border-bottom: 1px solid #eee;
  }

  .toc a {
    color: #667eea;
    text-decoration: none;
  }

  section {
    margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
  }

  section h2 {
    font-size: 1.75rem;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    color: #333;
  }

  section p {
    color: #555;
    line-height: 1.8;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .benchmark-table {
    overflow-x: auto;
    margin: 1.5rem 0;
  }

  table {
    width: 100%;
    border-collapse: collapse;
  }

  th, td {
    padding: 0.75rem;
    text-align: left;
    border-bottom: 1px solid #ddd;
  }

  th {
    background: #667eea;
    color: white;
  }

  tr:nth-child(even) {
    background: #f8f9fa;
  }

  ul {
    margin: 1rem 0;
    padding-left: 1.5rem;
  }

  li {
    margin: 0.5rem 0;
    color: #555;
  }

  .buy-links {
    text-align: center;
    margin-top: 2rem;
    padding: 2rem;
    background: #f8f9fa;
    border-radius: 12px;
  }

  .buy-btn {
    display: inline-block;
    padding: 1rem 3rem;
    background: #ff9900;
    color: white;
    text-decoration: none;
    border-radius: 8px;
    font-weight: 600;
    margin-top: 1rem;
  }

  .buy-btn:hover {
    background: #e68a00;
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .review-header h1 {
      font-size: 1.5rem;
    }
    
    .price-banner {
      flex-direction: column;
      gap: 0.5rem;
    }
  }
</style>
